  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimum Link is a lucid dreaming sandbox. Enter a world to start playing with it, spawning things into it, and the dream just might respond with things of its own.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 13 dream-like worlds to explore as your sandbox</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Single player, or invite a friend</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Atmospheric original soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Avatar customization</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Spawn things into the sandbox</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Adjust scale of things</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Telekinesis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Laser guns</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Spray paint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Enemies?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fish people</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Photo mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mouse and keyboard input method highly recommended.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>100% human-made. No AI was used in programming or asset generation for this product.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimum Link is a lucid dreaming sandbox. Enter a world to start playing with it, spawning things into it, and the dream just might respond with things of its own.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 13 dream-like worlds to explore as your sandbox</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Single player, or invite a friend</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Atmospheric original soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Avatar customization</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Spawn things into the sandbox</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Adjust scale of things</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Telekinesis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Laser guns</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Spray paint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Enemies?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fish people</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Photo mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mouse and keyboard input method highly recommended.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>100% human-made. No AI was used in programming or asset generation for this product.</i></p>",
